sequenceDiagram
    participant user
    participant browser
    participant server

    user->>browser: Writes note and clicks "Save"
    activate browser
    browser->>server: POST https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/exampleapp/new_note_spa
    Note right of browser:The browser sends a new note to the server
    activate server
    server-->>browser:  JSON data of the new note
    deactivate server
    deactivate browser

    Note right of browser: The browser updates the note list dynamically without reloading the page